I'm just gonna eat the collagen.

341
00:24:14,900 --> 00:24:16,500
You do the oddest things.

342
00:24:16,500 --> 00:24:20,070
Tomorrow let's go eat pork rinds.

343
00:24:20,070 --> 00:24:22,570
I really can't get any older.

344
00:24:24,640 --> 00:24:28,250
If that's your goal,
