345
00:24:28,250 --> 00:24:30,320
I'm drinking this because I'm sad.

346
00:24:30,320 --> 00:24:32,820
Anyhow you got your way back into
the movie scenes.

347
00:24:32,820 --> 00:24:35,390
You met your dad who you
had been missing so dearly.

348
00:24:35,390 --> 00:24:37,820
Why are you sad?

349
00:24:47,500 --> 00:24:49,670
Let's have a drink.

350
00:24:50,770 --> 00:24:53,410
You know I can't drink alcohol.

351
00:24:53,410 --> 00:24:56,740
What does it matter? Just us.

352
00:24:56,740 --> 00:25:01,250
Drink this and let it out.

353
