357
00:25:31,710 --> 00:25:33,780
Was it not lonely?

358
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:36,850
Yes, I did.

359
00:25:36,850 --> 00:25:43,290
It wasn't that lonely when I lived alone.

360
00:25:43,290 --> 00:25:49,530
However, after having a person to love
for the first time,

361
00:25:49,530 --> 00:25:53,070
realizing that I'll have to leave soon,

362
00:25:53,070 --> 00:25:56,570
it's now becoming very difficult.

363
00:25:56,570 --> 00:26:01,640
I feel like I'm the only one left in the world.

364
00:26:12,920 --> 00:26:21,630
If I go back, I’ll turn it back to

365
00:26:22,390 --> 00:26:25,230
the time before I met that person.

366
