Then I wouldn't be touched
regardless of how much he tried to move me.

367
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:33,040
I wouldn't like him.

368
00:26:33,770 --> 00:26:38,140
Just thinking about the days when he's not here,

369
00:26:38,140 --> 00:26:41,280
I feel like I going to die from loneliness.

370
