374
00:27:43,840 --> 00:27:45,880
What…

375
00:27:54,990 --> 00:27:58,290
Is it a blackout?

376
00:28:00,090 --> 00:28:02,030
Yoon-jae,

377
00:28:02,030 --> 00:28:04,160
look for some candles.

378
00:28:08,900 --> 00:28:12,140
What is this?

379
00:28:12,140 --> 00:28:15,140
I shouldn't have given him any alcohol.

380
00:28:15,140 --> 00:28:19,510
I thought he would only make some
objects move or something.

381
00:28:19,510 --> 00:28:22,450
Things have gotten out of control.

382
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:28,650
There isn't much time left.

383
00:28:28,650 --> 00:28:30,490
What?

384
00:28:32,260 --> 00:28:35,690
Why must I be here?

385
00:28:35,690 --> 00:28:45,470
Why must I... be with you
wasting this precious time?

386
00:28:45,470 --> 00:28:51,540
This is not what I want to be.

387
00:28:51,540 --> 00:28:59,690
I think one second is precious now.

388
00:28:59,690 --> 00:29:03,590
Why would I…

389
00:29:04,220 --> 00:29:06,760
Be here with you?

390
00:29:07,990 --> 00:29:11,730
This is not where I want to stay.

391
00:29:13,030 --> 00:29:16,640
Not here.

392
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:19,170
Damn.

393
00:29:19,170 --> 00:29:23,710
So you speak from your heart when you're drunk.

394
00:29:23,710 --> 00:29:26,680
Now I know your true feelings.

395
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:29,510
30 years of friendship means nothing

396
00:29:29,510 --> 00:29:32,250
