397
00:29:34,290 --> 00:29:35,250
What?

398
00:29:37,390 --> 00:29:40,260
What are you doing over there?

399
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:45,530
What are you doing?

400
00:29:45,530 --> 00:29:47,730
Move!

401
00:29:47,730 --> 00:29:48,430
What?

402
00:29:48,430 --> 00:29:51,870
I came out to see Cheon Song-yi's face.

403
00:29:51,870 --> 00:29:55,340
What are you doing over there, you hypocrite!

404
00:29:55,340 --> 00:29:58,040
Move! That's Cheon Song-yi's spot!

405
00:29:58,040 --> 00:30:02,050
Stop. Let's go inside.

406
00:30:07,950 --> 00:30:09,960
Can't you find a better place to use your power?

407
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:13,830
What the heck…

408
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:20,800
What the heck…

409
00:30:23,540 --> 00:30:27,610
I shouldn't have made him drink.
