410
00:30:27,610 --> 00:30:29,710
Move!

411
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:48,560
Oh my gosh.

412
00:30:55,070 --> 00:30:58,300
When did you come in?
Who told you that you could be here?

413
00:31:02,810 --> 00:31:04,910
Wake up right now!

414
00:31:05,910 --> 00:31:08,250
Leave!

415
00:31:08,950 --> 00:31:13,690
One, two, three!

416
00:31:13,690 --> 00:31:15,590
Well…

417
00:31:22,130 --> 00:31:25,230
You still don't get it?

418
00:31:27,270 --> 00:31:30,700
You leave me no choice then. I've tried.

419
00:31:38,610 --> 00:31:40,180
What happened?

420
00:31:40,180 --> 00:31:42,950
He said that he never drinks.

421
00:31:44,620 --> 00:31:51,190
I don't want to be with you, Lawyer Jang.

422
00:31:51,190 --> 00:31:53,260
I…

423
00:31:53,260 --> 00:31:54,960
I…

424
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:56,960
I…

425
00:31:58,530 --> 00:32:01,230
With whom?

426
00:32:02,630 --> 00:32:05,170
Who do you want to be with?

427
00:32:05,170 --> 00:32:08,840
Cheon Song-yi.

