00:32:46,950 --> 00:32:50,180
Sleeping somewhere other than
their home after getting drunk.

432
00:32:50,180 --> 00:32:52,920
Can’t remember anything
he has done the night before.

433
00:32:54,350 --> 00:32:56,660
What makes a human?

