I don't remember that well.

448
00:33:45,870 --> 00:33:48,140
Did I do that?

449
00:33:50,080 --> 00:33:51,710
I couldn't have done that.

450
00:33:52,380 --> 00:33:55,210
I don’t remember anything.

451
00:33:57,380 --> 00:34:00,990
That's why you said you wouldn't drink
