452
00:34:00,990 --> 00:34:05,260
You teleport to anywhere you want.

453
00:34:05,260 --> 00:34:08,429
You don't even remember what happened.

454
00:34:08,429 --> 00:34:09,260
You…

455
00:34:10,500 --> 00:34:11,860
Stay a little farther.

456
00:34:12,460 --> 00:34:13,030
You're...

457
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:14,400
I'm what?

458
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:15,429
I

459
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:19,710
can't think straight.

