482
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:19,930
Just let me rest!

483
00:35:19,930 --> 00:35:22,100
You're so cheap!

484
00:35:22,100 --> 00:35:23,500
What? Why aren't you leaving?

485
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:24,800
Do your teleport thing.

486
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:25,970
Go!

487
00:35:25,970 --> 00:35:27,170
That…

488
00:35:27,910 --> 00:35:29,040
