00:36:28,570 --> 00:36:29,840
Who were you talking to?

509
00:36:32,340 --> 00:36:33,510
Talk to whom?

510
00:36:33,510 --> 00:36:34,810
What are you talking about?

511
00:36:34,810 --> 00:36:37,110
You were talking to yourself like that?

512
00:36:37,110 --> 00:36:38,410
That's strange.

513
00:36:38,410 --> 00:36:41,010
