516
00:36:42,750 --> 00:36:44,280
Ah, right. Yoon-jae,

517
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,720
did you try calling dad?

518
00:36:45,720 --> 00:36:47,920
I gave you his number a while ago.

519
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:49,020
I told you,

520
00:36:49,020 --> 00:36:50,190
he's your dad,

521
00:36:50,190 --> 00:36:51,890
