526
00:36:59,130 --> 00:37:02,030
And no matter how awkward, our dad is our dad.

527
00:37:02,030 --> 00:37:04,170
You think you were dropped from the sky?

528
00:37:04,170 --> 00:37:06,100
Hey. Are you some sort of an alien?

529
00:37:07,010 --> 00:37:07,910
Hi.

530
00:37:26,060 --> 00:37:27,190
Hello.

531
00:37:33,130 --> 00:37:34,400
Hi.

532
00:37:41,410 --> 00:37:42,840
[Sky Mental Hospital]

533
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:49,550
